Chanell Stone bụ onye Amerịka na-ese foto
Ọ bụ onye ojii amara ya maka usoro "Natura Negra". Stone bi ma na-arụ ọrụ na Oakland, California.
O nwetara akara ugo mmụta na Bekee na Los Angeles Trade-Technical College n'afọ 2017
Stone nwetara akara ugo mmụta BFA na foto na California College of the Arts n'afọ 2019.
Ọrụ Chanell Stone na-egosipụtakarị ihe osise onwe onye ojii na nke ọcha
O bu ụzọ were klas foto analog na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ma nọgide na-eji ihe nkiri eme ihe n'omume ya, ọkachasị na-agba égbè na Pentax.

Stone bụ onye na-ese foto na W Magazine's "Ndị a bụ ndị na-ese foto asatọ na-eto eto ga-eso n'afọ 2020". Ọ bụkwa onye ikpeazụ edepụtara maka 2020 San Francisco Artadia Award. Ọ na-ekwu na mmasị ya na nnọchi anya na eserese onwe ya na-etolite na mgbasa ozi ọha na eze, ya bụ Myspace. Foto foto na-aga n'ihu ịbụ isi ihe ọ na-elekwasị anya.
